title: Optimize UI for Android 3.0 and above.
message:
Optimize UI for Android 3.0 and above.
Change version string to 1.1.0.0.
Change version code to 2.

title: Try to restore CVS daemon status after SDCard is mounted.
message:
Try to restore CVS daemon status after SDCard is mounted.
Use Environment.getExternalStorageDirectory() instead of hard code "/sdcard".
